purpose "Combine Jellyfish databases for use with error correcter"
package "combine_jf_dbs"

description "N databases are merged, read in order of appearence on
the command line. The lowest quality k-mers are in the first database
and the highest quality k-mers are in the last.

The output database contains for every k-mer the number of the highest
quality database containing this k-mer and its count in this
database.

All the databases must use the same k-mer size, max reprobe value and
hash function (matrix)."

# option("thread", "t") {
